                                                                        Monitoring Metrics

    Server metrics:
        1)	CPU
            -	CPU used
            -	CPU load
            -	CPU temperature
        2)	Memory usage
        3)	I/O
            -	Disk space usage
            -	IO read, IO write
        4)	Network
            -	Network traffic
            -	TCP connection states
        5)	Sever state (Running/Stopped)

    Application metrics:
        1)	SSL certificates validate status
